    "Ideally, the retention evalu-ation should encompass all possible knowledge except that to be forgotten.",
    "Nonetheless, this is unfeasible in most cases, given the wide range of capabilities that LLMs can learn.",
    "Instead, researchers define the forgetting test set by selecting the subset of the most relevant tasks for which utility should be retained.",
    "In the following, we list the most prominent strategies used to measure the retained utility:",
    "• General benchmarks."
